Type of API:

1. REST (Rest full API)
2. RPC (Remote Procedure)
3. SOAP (Simple object Access Protocol)

# HTTP Protocol

# HTTP Methods
->  GET (Retrieve information)
->  POST (Add new entry to database)
->  PUT (Update existing information)
->  PATCH (Update specific details of existing data)
->  DELETE (Delete the information)

Response Code
100 - 199 :  Informational response code
200 - 299 :  Success of Operation
300 - 399 :  Re-directional operation
400 - 499 :  Client Errors
500 - 599 :  Server Errors

# Manual Testing
-> We have to use tool called postman.


